Ranger Help for: learn
======================

SYNTAX:      learn
             learn <skill>
             learn cost <skill>
USAGE:       Any wilderness terrain.

SUMMARY:
The learn command is how Rangers acquire new skills.

  learn              Shows all skills you know about, marking which
                     are learned and which are available to learn.
  learn <skill>      Learn a skill. Costs slots only.
  learn cost <skill> Shows the exact cost, prerequisites, terrains,
                     and what the skill unlocks.

Skills have prerequisites - you must learn earlier skills to unlock
later ones. When you learn a skill, any new skills it unlocks will
automatically appear in your available list.

Your first available skill is 'forage'. Start there.

